OUTPUT
------

- word size: 32-bit

- first two words:
    * size of text section
    * size of data section

- text section
    * binary instructions
    * the length must be equal to the specified text section length

- data section
    * initial values of variables



EXAMPLE
-------

<text section size>
<data section size>
<instruction 1>
    ...
<instruction n>
<value 1>
    ...
<value n>
